{
  "stem": "5375.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He used to bring me dinner every night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He used to bring me my ration bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[SIGHS] But I was already so sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was burning up in fever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I didn't know already about myself, but he was still to throw the bread, mopped my head.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was, you know, like-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I didn't know about myself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was going on for about maybe a week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The dysentery-- it was going out of you, only [? pus. ?] I didn't have no time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because it was, by the door, it was no bathroom, or anything like that, or latrines.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] By the door, it was a big pile of straw.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the people who had the time to run until there-- they made it in the straw, and that's all.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But nobody cleaned it away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Everything was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In the morning, they used to come and collect the dead bodies out on the railway tracks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And, of course, they used to bury them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was here, the diseased barrack, about-- until I wake up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I wake up slowly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It took me about two days to come back from coma, like-- it was like-- I was, like in a coma.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Hungry like a dog.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Somehow, I put my hands-- I'm looking around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "My head is on something, like on a rock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I am-- putting my hands.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And whatever I found there in the dark, I'm putting it in my mouth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I see it's old bread, stale bread, what my friend throw it to my head.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I found the bread there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "For about three or four days, I was eating the bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
